#       ** Notes.......:                                                      #
#                       - This config file is for a plasma +i3wm setup        #
#                         - comment out the plasma section for i3wm only      #
#                                                                             #
#       ** Dependencies:                                                      #
#                       - kitty terminal                                      #
#                       - Hack font                                           #
#                       - Rofi                                                #
#                       - Plasma                                              #
#                       - VScodium                                            #
#                       - Slack                                               #
#                       - Firefox                                             #
#                       - Discord                                             #
#                       - Telegram                                            #
#                       - Signal                                              #
